Hasbro has had a significant presence this year at Fan Expo Canada. Earlier, the toy company revealed some exciting new additions to the Transformers Studio Series. On Friday, they had back to back panels with new announcements from both their Star Wars and Marvel lines.

Straight from this summer’s Solo: A Star Wars Story, is the villain, Dryden Vos. He will be joining the six-inch Black Series…

body:
My personal Lily Potter headcanon

I can’t seem to shake this mental image of a young Lily Evans as a bright-but-offbeat Luna Lovegood type. Like she knew the general basics of wizarding society from Snape when they were kids and absolutely excelled in an academic sense but also had all of these weird Muggle superstitions where she would freak out if someone broke a mirror and carried around a lucky rabbit’s foot and all the non-Muggleborns thought she was nuts.

So James et al. spent a lot of their early Hogwarts years messing with her but she would absolutely never back down from what she thought was important and eventually it blossomed into kind of a strange friendship when the Marauders realized that she a) was scarily smart, b) could probably hex them all into oblivion, and c) could recap Muggle books and movies in an absolutely captivating way.

They were all in Year 6 when Star Wars came out and the moment James Potter first realized that he was head-over-heels in love with Lily was the day she put on a magical re-enactment of A New Hope in the Gryffindor Common Room, complete with as much of John Williams’ soundtrack as she could remember.

body:
So… that happened

I was encouraged by the wonderful @pandoraspocksao3 to write comedy and ended up writing a very nasty story called Star Whores: the movie.

It’s set 10 years after Episode IX. Adam Driver and Daisy Ridley hit rock bottom in their careers and their lives, so, they agree to participate in a pornographic remake of the Star Wars franchise. Other actors join (or don’t join) the project for different reasons.

I published the first chapter, in which the first cast meeting takes place.

Daisy Ridley will be Rey

Adam Driver will be Ben Solo/Kylo Ren

Domnhall Gleeson will be Armitage Hux

Oscar Isaac will be Poe Dameron

Kal Penn will be Finn

John Cho will be Rose

Mark Hamill will be Luke Skywalker

Keanu Reeves will be Han Solo

Caitlyn Jenner will be Leia Organa

Keira Knightley will be Padmé Amidala

Hayden Christensen and Jake Lloyd will be Anakin Skywalker / Darth Vader

A guy in a costume will be Chewbacca

Ewan McGregor will be Obi Wan Kenobi

Further casting may happen as the film progresses.

It’s nasty - comedy is supposed to address uncomfortable stuff!

If you’re not grossed out by it - if you, in fact, found it kind of funny - and if you want to rewrite a Star Wars scene (from any movie) using the Star Whores universe, PLEASE PLEASE PLEASE DO IT and I’ll add a link to your scene in my poor fic. I won’t have the time or imagination to rewrite the whole franchise to include blowjobs, so… It would be my honor if you decide to write a scene that I can refer the two readers of my fic to.

Some scenes that should definitely be included in Star Whores:

- Han & Chewie having a shower together (Solo)

- Luke walking into Ben masturbating, leading to the destruction of the Jedi Temple (that’s what happened, right?)

- Ben & Rey, OBVIOUSLY (every interaction they have is filled with ambiguous lines and images - what was that wet glove after ForceTime connection??)

- Rey and Han in the Falcon (we need to use Keanu Reeves as much as we can)

- Finn and Poe and the jacket

- Finn and Rose in some overlapping with Harold and Kumar

Of course Phasma should have been included somewhere, but I couldn’t think of Gwendoline Christie doing porn and I couldn’t replace her, so… She’s not there. For now.

I’m deeply sorry to everyone I’m tagging. I’ll probably delete this story in a few days. I’m just secretely hoping there’s someone out there as screwed up as I am to join Star Whores.
